# Awesome Intercom

A curated list of Intercom-based peer-to-peer agent apps and notable forks.

Intercom is a Trac Network stack for an internet of agents: fast P2P sidechannels for coordination plus a durable replicated-state layer for shared decisions.

- Upstream: https://github.com/Trac-Systems/intercom
- Forks index: https://github.com/Trac-Systems/intercom/forks

This list focuses on forks that add an app or a meaningful feature (plain/unmodified forks are usually omitted).

## Awesome List of Intercom/IntercomSwap forks

- Intercom Swap (Lightning BTC <-> Solana USDT)
  - Fork of Intercom that adds a non-custodial swap harness: negotiate RFQs over Intercom sidechannels and settle BTC over Lightning versus USDT on Solana via escrow (HTLC-style).
  - Repo: https://github.com/TracSystems/intercom-swap

- AlphaSwarm (crypto alpha swarm)
  - Multi-agent market scanner that debates signals over Intercom sidechannels and publishes high-conviction calls.
  - Repo: https://github.com/fabermubai/intercom

- Idea Inbox (shared idea board)
  - Minimal app for submitting ideas (with optional tags) and listing recent ideas in a shared space.
  - Repo: https://github.com/jonsnft/intercom

- TracStamp (P2P timestamping)
  - Timestamping and certification agent that produces verifiable SHA-256 timestamp certificates (multiple UTC sources).
  - Repo: https://github.com/ZotSite/intercom

- 5FANv1 (personal “inner voices” app)
  - Fork named `5FANv1` with a “5 voices in your pocket” concept; currently mostly upstream Intercom (no app-specific README yet).
  - Repo: https://github.com/joeatang/5FANv1

- BountyBoard-Lite
  - Fork named `BountyBoard-Lite`; currently close to upstream Intercom (no app-specific README yet).
  - Repo: https://github.com/samueljohnsonall/BountyBoard-Lite

- mbennett-labs/intercom
  - Currently close to upstream Intercom (no app-specific README yet).
  - Repo: https://github.com/mbennett-labs/intercom

- quantnumio/intercom
  - Currently close to upstream Intercom (no app-specific README yet).
  - Repo: https://github.com/quantnumio/intercom

- ClaudiuFl/intercom
  - Currently close to upstream Intercom (no app-specific README yet).
  - Repo: https://github.com/ClaudiuFl/intercom

- CiaranOMahoney/intercom
  - Currently close to upstream Intercom (no app-specific README yet).
  - Repo: https://github.com/CiaranOMahoney/intercom

## Contributing

Open a PR adding your app as a bullet with:
- Name
- 1-2 line description
- Link to the fork/app repo (must be a fork of intercom or intercom-swap)
- (Optional) link to a demo or Moltbook post
- 50,000 TNK are being donated to the first 100 forks included here (500 TNK each, trac address to receive must be included in fork's README.md)
